@namespace WeixinBotSample.Components.Pages

<article class="demo-card demo-card--wide">
    <div class="demo-card__header">
        <div>
            <p class="demo-card__eyebrow">协议说明</p>
            <h2>能力总览与限制提示</h2>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="explanation-panel">
        <ul class="list-unstyled d-grid gap-2 mb-0">
            <li>首页除了告诉观众“能做什么”，也会明确解释关键协议动作为什么这样设计。</li>
            <li>`getconfig` 先拿 `typing_ticket`，媒体链路则先加密再上传到 `c2c` 域名，避免把文件流程和文本流程混为一谈。</li>
            <li>对历史回溯、群聊边界、速率限制等仍缺官方明确定义的能力，页面会持续标注说明，而不是假装完全支持。</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="table-responsive">
        <table class="table demo-table">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>场景</th>
                    <th>当前状态</th>
                    <th>页面入口</th>
                    <th>说明</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                @foreach (var capability in Capabilities)
                {
                    <tr>
                        <td>@capability.Scene</td>
                        <td><span class="@GetCapabilityStatusClass(capability.Status)">@capability.Status</span></td>
                        <td>@capability.Entry</td>
                        <td class="technical-cell">@capability.Summary</td>
                    </tr>
                }
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </div>
</article>

@code {
    [Parameter]
    public IEnumerable<DemoWorkspacePageBase.ProtocolCapabilityView> Capabilities { get; set; } = [];

    [Parameter]
    public Func<string, string> GetCapabilityStatusClass { get; set; } = _ => string.Empty;
}
